
# css-rtl.pl - a CSS LTR ? RTL converter
# Copyright Ahmad AlTwaijiry 2011 (Inspired by r2 https://github.com/ded/r2)
# https://github.com/mrahmadt/
# License MIT

Simple script to convert any normal CSS file (left to right direction) to RTL (right to left direction).


To use the script:

./css-rtl.pl INPUT-CSS-FILE.CSS         <--- this will print the changes to STDOUT


./css-rtl.pl INPUT-CSS-FILE.CSS OUTPUT-CSS-FILE.CSS     <--- save changes to the file OUTPUT-CSS-FILE.CSS
